h3. Summary

When using the Quick Create Issue after reaching a *Project Does Not Exist* page, both the *Project* and *Issue Type* fields will show as duplicates.

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Navigate to a valid issue;
# Change the URL to a non existant project key;
# The *Project Does Not Exist* page will be displayed;
# Click on *Create* to open the issue creation panel;

h3. Expected Results

Only one field for *Project* and *Issue Type* will be presented.

h3. Actual Results

The *Create Issue* panel will present duplicate fields for *Project* and *Issue Type*.

